onest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William de Montifichet was born in 1204, in Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland as the son of William de Montifichet. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1241, in his hometown, at the age of 37, and was buried in Scotland."},"et":{"1204–1241":"1204–1241","1206–1267":"1206–1267","1226–1287":"1226–1287","1165–1215":"1165–1215","1206":"1206","1204":"1204","26 March 1215":"26. märts 1215","1215":"1215","1226":"1226","1267":"1267","1287":"1287","1165":"1165","1241":"1241","Scotland":"Scotland","Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland":"Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland"},"fi":{"1204–1241":"1204–1241","1206–1267":"1206–1267","1226–1287":"1226–1287","1165–1215":"1165–1215","1206":"1206","1204":"1204","26 March 1215":"26. maaliskuuta 1215","1215":"1215","1226":"1226","1267":"1267","1287":"1287","1165":"1165","1241":"1241","Scotland":"Scotland","Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland":"Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland"},"fr":{"1204–1241":"1204–1241","1206–1267":"1206–1267","1226–1287":"1226–1287","1165–1215":"1165–1215","1206":"1206","1204":"1204","26 March 1215":"26 mars 1215","1215":"1215","1226":"1226","1267":"1267","1287":"1287","1165":"1165","1241":"1241","Scotland":"Écosse","Cargill, Perthshire, Scotland":"Cargill, Perthshire, Écosse","lifeSummary":"William de Montifichet est né en 1204, à Cargill, Perthshire, Écosse, fils de William de Montifichet. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1241, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 37 ans, et a été enterré à Écosse."},"de":{"1204–1241":"1204–1241","1206–1267":"1206–1267","1226–1287":"1226–1287","1165–1215":"1165–1215","1206":"1206","1204":"1204","26 March 1215":"26. März 1215","1215":"1215","1226":"1226","1267":"1267","1287":"1287","1165":"1165","1241":"1241","Scotland":"Scotland","Cargill, Perthshire, Scotlan